### GEOMETRY
/Geometry/NextTonScale/active_diam 300. cm
/Geometry/NextTonScale/active_length 300. cm
/Geometry/NextTonScale/fcage_thickn 1. cm
/Geometry/NextTonScale/ics_thickn 12. cm
/Geometry/NextTonScale/gas_density 89. kg/m3


### GENERATOR
# Single Particle
/Generator/SingleParticle/particle nu_e
/Generator/SingleParticle/min_energy 1. GeV
/Generator/SingleParticle/max_energy 1. GeV
/Generator/SingleParticle/region ACTIVE
/Generator/SingleParticle/momentum_X 0.
/Generator/SingleParticle/momentum_Y 0.
/Generator/SingleParticle/momentum_Z 1.


### ACTIONS
/Actions/DefaultEventAction/energy_threshold 2.3 MeV


### PHYSICS (For fast Simulation)
/PhysicsList/Nexus/clustering           false
/PhysicsList/Nexus/drift                false
/PhysicsList/Nexus/electroluminescence  false


### VERBOSITIES
/control/verbose 0
/run/verbose 0
/event/verbose 0
/tracking/verbose 1


### JOB CONTROL
/nexus/random_seed 1
/nexus/persistency/hdf5 true
/nexus/persistency/start_id 0
/nexus/persistency/outputFile NextTon.next
